Roadmap

Phase	Tasks
Phase 1: Learning	Complete. Build a basic multiplayer prototype.
Phase 2: Core Game	Implement player movement, shooting, AI enemies, and loot system.
Phase 3: Polish	Add atmosphere, objectives, and survival mechanics.
Phase 4: Expand	Add more features (anomalies, artifacts, larger map).
Phase 5: Release	Test, optimize, and release a small co-op experience.
